<div class="text">
<p dir="ltr">Many people use Bitcoin as an investment, buying the cryptocurrency in an attempt to gain a profit on its fluctuation. Others view it simply as a new way of spending money. The number of places where you can spend your Bitcoins is growing every day. Here is what you can spend your Bitcoins on:</p>

<h2>Online<a id="online" name="online"></a></h2>
<h3>List of major online merchants<a id="list-of-major-online-merchants" name="list-of-major-online-merchants"></a></h3>
<ul>
 	<li><a href="http://overstock.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Overstock</a>Â â€” Â the first large online retailer to accept and fully support Bitcoin payments. You can buy anything from furniture to laptops and television sets.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.newegg.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Newegg</a>Â â€” an electronic retail giant is accepting Bitcoin payments for most of its stock.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://shopify.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Shopify</a>Â â€” an e-commerce platform that allows users to create their own online stores similar to Etsy and eBay.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.etsy.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Etsy</a>Â â€” around 100 vendors accept Bitcoin payments now.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/13942/microsoft-account-add-money-with-bitcoin" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Microsoft</a>Â â€” one of the biggest companies in the world allows users to add money to their accounts with Bitcoin.</li>
</ul>
Most major online retailers are still not accepting Bitcoins as a form of payment, but there is a way of buying products from them using only digital currency. See the Gift Cards section below.
<h3>List of aggregators<a id="list-of-aggregators" name="list-of-aggregators"></a></h3>
<ul>
 	<li><a href="http://www.wheretospendbitcoins.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Where To Spend Bitcoins UK</a>Â â€” a directory of shops, pubs, websites and other places in the UK that accept Bitcoins.</li>
 	<li><a href="http://usebitcoins.info/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">useBitcoins</a>Â â€” a platform with almost 5,000 listed businesses that accept BTC.</li>
 	<li><a href="http://www.coinmap.org/welcome/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Coinmap</a>Â â€” a map of Bitcoin-accepting businesses worldwide.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://spendabit.co/?r=bitcoin.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Spendabit</a>Â â€” a search engine capable of finding specific good available to buy for Bitcoins.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Services<a id="services" name="services"></a></h3>
Bitcoinâ€™s acceptance as a payment option depends on a particular companyâ€™s decision. Hence, there are no specific markets where BTC is universally accepted. Instead, there are various companies in different sectors of services looking to expand their client bases by introducing digital currencies as a new payment option.
<ul>
 	<li><a href="https://www.dish.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Dish Network</a>Â â€” an American direct-broadcast satellite service provider.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.expressvpn.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">ExpressVPN</a>Â â€” high speed, secure VPN network.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.expressvpn.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">PureVPN</a>Â â€” high speed, secure VPN network.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.okcupid.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">OKCupid</a>Â â€” online dating website.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://ru.wordpress.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">WordPress</a>Â â€” an online company that allows users to create websites and blogs.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.reddit.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Reddit</a>Â â€” you can buy premium features with Bitcoins.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.namecheap.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Namecheap</a>Â â€” domain name register.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Bloomberg</a>,Â <a href="https://chicago.suntimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Chicago Sun-Times</a>, etc â€” online-newspaper subscription for Bitcoins.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://www.suicidegirls.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">SuicideGirls</a>Â â€” a popular adult-themed community now accepts Bitcoins for a subscription.</li>
 	<li><a href="https://teamtreehouse.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Treehouse</a>Â â€” an online interactive education specialist, accepting Bitcoin for a variety of courses.</li>
</ul>
