<h3>Taxi<a id="taxi" name="taxi"></a></h3>
There are several taxi dispatch services as well as airport transportation services in various parts of the world that accept Bitcoin payment. Hereâ€™s aÂ <a href="http://spendbitcoins.com/places/c/taxis/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">mappable list</a>Â of such companies.
