<h2>Bullion traders<a id="bullion-traders" name="bullion-traders"></a></h2>
<p dir="ltr">For those who prefer to store their funds in a heavy, physical form there are companies such asÂ <a href="https://www.goldmoney.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">BitGold</a>, which specializes in utilizing gold for payments and savings, including Bitcoin. There is also a company calledÂ <a href="https://www.amagimetals.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Amagi Metals</a>, which has been trading Bitcoins for precious metals since 2012.</p>

